name: Linguriboh
desc:
1 Level 4 or lower Cyberse monster
When your opponent activates a Trap Card (Quick Effect): You can Tribute this card; negate the effect, and if you do, banish that card. If this card is in your GY (Quick Effect): You can Tribute 1 "@Ignister" monster that was Special Summoned from the Extra Deck; Special Summon this card. You can only use each effect of "Linguriboh" once per turn.
